INSTALL-JQUERYUI

The plugin Jquery UI for roundcube is needed if you must use jQuery datepicker
to select vacation start / end dates.

- Download it from his website : http://code.google.com/p/roundcube-plugins/

- Copy and extract the plugin archive in plugins/ directory of your roundcube
  installation.

- Activate the plugin in config/main.inc.php :

  	// List of active plugins (in plugins/ directory)
	$rcmail_config['plugins'] = array('jqueryui', 'vacation');

- The jQuery datepickers will be shown for the vacation start/end.
